Fiona (singer) https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Fiona_(singer) 0 Fiona Eileen Flanagan (born September 13, 1961), known by the stage name Fiona, is an American rock music singer-songwriter and actress best known as the love interest in the 1987 Bob Dylan vehicle, Hearts of Fire.
